## How to Run

1. Create a MySQL database and run `retail_sales_analysis.sql` ‚Äî it will create all 5 tables, insert the raw data, and run all 10 analysis queries in order.
2. Alternatively, load the individual CSV files into any tool of your choice (Excel, Power BI, pandas) if you only need the raw data without the schema or queries.

